# apeFEA

A modular nonlinear finite element framework for structural analysis, focused on Pythonic clarity, extendability, and research-oriented workflows.

## Features
- Material and geometric nonlinearity
- Modular geometry definition
- Configurable DOF and dimensions
- Node management and plotting
